WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.980
[Episode 25]

02:50.710 --> 02:51.560
Qi Feng.

02:52.470 --> 02:54.610
You don't really hate Fan Yue, do you?

02:54.640 --> 02:55.780
Shut up.

02:55.890 --> 02:57.380
But sometimes,

02:57.670 --> 02:58.790
hatred is more powerful

02:59.040 --> 03:00.870
than love to make a person go on living.

03:01.180 --> 03:02.940
You've been suffering a lot these years.

03:02.970 --> 03:05.250
If you hadn't had a way to vent your anger,

03:05.270 --> 03:06.500
you may not have persisted.

03:07.400 --> 03:08.630
But the Baize Clan doesn't exist anymore,

03:08.630 --> 03:10.370
and the Tiger Clan has been eliminated. There's no one you can blame.

03:10.390 --> 03:11.900
The only one you can hate now

03:12.030 --> 03:13.840
is Fan Yue who is still alive.

03:13.860 --> 03:14.580
You hate him

03:14.610 --> 03:15.730
because you care about him.

03:15.750 --> 03:16.660
You can't forget him.

03:16.690 --> 03:17.540
That's enough!

03:19.110 --> 03:20.240
You think you're quite smart

03:20.280 --> 03:21.520
and can read people's minds?

03:21.720 --> 03:24.240
I did this to get back at him

03:24.260 --> 03:25.340
and torture him.

03:25.360 --> 03:26.700
When he feels guilty enough

03:26.770 --> 03:28.020
and suffers enough pain,

03:28.110 --> 03:29.670
I'll surely kill him.

03:31.090 --> 03:31.880
Qi Feng.

03:32.680 --> 03:33.640
Stop it.

03:33.780 --> 03:35.660
He's been suffering a lot all these years, too.

03:36.090 --> 03:37.850
He also wants to try his best to compensate you.

03:39.020 --> 03:40.230
He wants to compensate me?

03:40.310 --> 03:41.780
If he really wants to compensate me,

03:41.800 --> 03:43.700
he should have killed Cang Shan for me!

03:44.880 --> 03:46.280
But the truth is that

03:46.650 --> 03:48.490
in his mind, I'm even less important than you

03:48.520 --> 03:49.740
and Cang Shan!

03:50.350 --> 03:51.840
He feels guilty?

03:52.070 --> 03:53.320
He wants to compensate me?

03:53.350 --> 03:55.050
It's all fake!

03:55.650 --> 03:57.920
He's with Cang Shan now.

03:58.600 --> 04:00.390
How could you miss

04:00.560 --> 04:02.130
such a good show?

04:12.360 --> 04:13.310
Master.

04:13.460 --> 04:15.400
What... What's wrong with you, Master?

04:15.690 --> 04:16.570
Master.

04:17.130 --> 04:18.810
I'm Cang Shan, Master.

04:19.500 --> 04:20.510
Master.

04:22.320 --> 04:23.640
I'm Cang Shan.

04:25.500 --> 04:26.950
I'm Cang Shan.

04:28.000 --> 04:28.630
Master.

04:34.970 --> 04:36.180
Master.

04:39.880 --> 04:41.050
Master!

04:41.080 --> 04:42.200
Wake up!

04:46.909 --> 04:47.659
Fan Yue!

04:47.680 --> 04:48.530
Stop!

04:48.560 --> 04:49.670
He's Cang Shan!

04:50.760 --> 04:52.720
Master, wake up.

05:07.120 --> 05:09.070
He's indeed the Demon King of the Polar Region.

05:09.100 --> 05:11.060
Under the control of the parent insect,

05:11.080 --> 05:13.490
he could even awaken a bit of his consciousness.

05:14.150 --> 05:15.480
You brought me here forcibly

05:15.500 --> 05:17.770
so that I could watch Fan Yue kill Cang Shan with my own eyes, huh?

05:19.180 --> 05:20.550
Isn't it interesting?

05:22.690 --> 05:23.500
Let go of her!

05:48.130 --> 05:50.130
Since you can't bear to kill Cang Shan,

05:50.159 --> 05:52.340
then just kill the person you love by yourself!

05:54.860 --> 05:55.659
Fan Yue.

05:55.680 --> 05:58.100
Cut her and take the Contemplation Stone out of her body for me!

06:04.610 --> 06:05.930
Master, no!

06:19.380 --> 06:21.120
Take the evil insects out and awaken Master Fan.

06:21.630 --> 06:22.830
Otherwise, I'll kill you.

06:25.060 --> 06:26.170
Just kill me.

06:26.740 --> 06:28.930
If you kill me, upon my death,

06:28.950 --> 06:31.220
the parent insect in his body will become wilder.

06:31.330 --> 06:33.720
Then your Master Fan will never wake up.

06:35.000 --> 06:36.430
If you go save her,

06:36.630 --> 06:38.830
all the members of the Stone Clan will die.

07:01.480 --> 07:03.450
Fan Yue, wake up!

07:03.480 --> 07:04.530
I'm Bai Shuo!

07:08.270 --> 07:10.310
Qi Feng, I was the one who broke your legs.

07:10.360 --> 07:11.390
They are innocent.

07:11.390 --> 07:12.270
Spare them.

07:12.290 --> 07:14.820
Cang Shan, if you want to save your clansmen,

07:14.860 --> 07:16.720
I'll give you a chance.

07:17.500 --> 07:18.810
Kill Fan Yue.

07:19.470 --> 07:21.270
Then I will spare the people of the Stone Clan.

07:24.800 --> 07:26.440
Don't be controlled by the evil insects!

07:26.460 --> 07:27.620
Wake up!

07:30.320 --> 07:31.320
What?

07:31.760 --> 07:32.890
You don't want to do that?

07:33.370 --> 07:35.010
Then I'll let you see them die

07:35.040 --> 07:37.909
one by one in front of you.

07:41.390 --> 07:42.800
Qi Feng!

07:49.950 --> 07:51.480
If you kill Fan Yue,

07:52.159 --> 07:53.880
you can save everyone.

08:15.690 --> 08:17.370
I'll compensate you with my life.

08:19.490 --> 08:20.540
If I die,

08:22.080 --> 08:23.740
I think your hatred will be over.

08:26.050 --> 08:28.370
Please spare Master Fan and Bai Shuo.

08:30.400 --> 08:32.620
Please spare the people of the Stone Clan!

08:32.909 --> 08:33.960
Sparing them?

08:34.610 --> 08:36.750
If it was that easy to spare others,

08:36.770 --> 08:38.900
why didn't anyone spare the Baize Clan

08:38.919 --> 08:40.120
and me back then?

08:40.970 --> 08:42.610
Did we deserve to die?

08:46.910 --> 08:47.910
Fan Yue.

08:48.030 --> 08:49.500
Do it quickly.

08:49.520 --> 08:50.830
Kill her

08:50.880 --> 08:52.420
and take the Contemplation Stone out of her body!

09:19.200 --> 09:20.270
Fan Yue.

09:20.380 --> 09:22.170
Is it my ending that

09:23.270 --> 09:24.960
I'll be killed by you?

09:23.350 --> 09:28.310
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

09:31.470 --> 09:37.080
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

09:39.790 --> 09:47.190
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

09:48.110 --> 09:53.300
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

09:58.320 --> 09:59.290
Cang Shan.

09:59.630 --> 10:01.310
The parent insect entered Cang Shan's body.

10:11.070 --> 10:12.280
Destroy all the evil insects!

10:12.300 --> 10:13.120
Stop it!

10:13.210 --> 10:14.490
If the parent insect doesn't die,

10:14.520 --> 10:15.910
the sub insect won't stop.

10:16.250 --> 10:17.490
You want to win?

10:17.520 --> 10:18.790
It's not that easy.

10:22.390 --> 10:24.130
Kill the three of them for me.

10:24.150 --> 10:25.320
Regardless of the cost,

10:25.350 --> 10:27.110
don't stop till they're dead!

10:27.140 --> 10:28.680
We can't let the people of the Stone Clan enter the center of the formation.

10:29.030 --> 10:30.120
Otherwise, with the harm of the evil insects

10:30.120 --> 10:31.510
and the erosion of Baize's resentment aura,

10:31.530 --> 10:32.920
they will all die from self-explosions.

10:33.710 --> 10:36.040
If they keep blocking it like this, they will eventually be exhausted.

10:36.060 --> 10:37.250
Today in this place,

10:37.280 --> 10:39.160
either the people of the Stone Clan will die

10:39.180 --> 10:40.940
or you'll be killed by the people of the Stone Clan.

10:40.970 --> 10:42.300
There isn't a third way.

10:42.850 --> 10:44.250
There must be an ending

10:44.280 --> 10:45.880
for all grudges.

10:59.400 --> 11:00.240
No.

11:00.590 --> 11:01.720
You are wrong.

11:01.900 --> 11:03.330
Our Stone Clan

11:03.400 --> 11:05.310
is best at cutting mountains to build roads.

11:06.330 --> 11:07.520
I'll create

11:08.580 --> 11:09.600
the third way.

11:20.550 --> 11:21.480
Cang Shan!

11:37.240 --> 11:38.220
Master.

11:38.370 --> 11:40.550
Take care of my clansmen for me.

11:41.370 --> 11:42.460
Cang Shan!

11:42.490 --> 11:43.760
Don't do anything stupid!

11:47.620 --> 11:48.710
Master!

11:49.550 --> 11:51.390
This is the best result.

11:51.410 --> 11:53.860
Only when I die with the parent insect

11:53.890 --> 11:56.440
may all these grudges be over.

12:07.570 --> 12:09.730
I've been away from home for a long time.

12:11.380 --> 12:13.590
My parents and clansmen are all here.

12:14.810 --> 12:16.330
Just let me stay here.

12:19.450 --> 12:21.000
It's a pity that

12:23.180 --> 12:25.620
I'm not able to see Tian Huo for the last time.

12:33.830 --> 12:36.020
Master Fan can live long without worries.

12:35.420 --> 12:40.740
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

12:36.170 --> 12:37.450
At the Bright Moon Palace,

12:37.770 --> 12:39.000
he's the best in the Demon Race.

12:39.120 --> 12:41.120
Cang Shan eats a lot every day.

12:41.170 --> 12:43.960
Tian Huo lives with me happily.

12:43.500 --> 12:49.050
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

12:44.290 --> 12:45.520
Cang Shan.

12:51.550 --> 12:58.920
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

12:57.760 --> 12:58.670
Cang Shan.

12:59.310 --> 13:04.090
♫I'm your wanderer♫

13:00.570 --> 13:01.450
Cang Shan!

13:09.200 --> 13:11.100
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

13:11.170 --> 13:13.220
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

13:13.400 --> 13:15.100
♫My love brought tears♫

13:15.320 --> 13:17.220
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

13:17.490 --> 13:19.470
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

13:19.630 --> 13:21.100
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

13:21.250 --> 13:22.840
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

13:23.300 --> 13:24.550
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

13:25.360 --> 13:26.880
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

13:27.470 --> 13:28.920
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

13:29.300 --> 13:31.120
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

13:31.510 --> 13:33.310
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

13:31.760 --> 13:33.200
Baize's resentment aura.

13:33.600 --> 13:35.360
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

13:35.580 --> 13:37.420
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

13:37.780 --> 13:39.350
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

13:39.620 --> 13:42.230
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

14:43.480 --> 14:44.750
Chong Zhao sent a message that

14:44.750 --> 14:47.110
there is an ancient mirror hidden in Zhen Yu's room.

14:45.360 --> 14:48.350
[There's an ancient bronze mirror with cracks in Zhen Yu's room.]

14:47.140 --> 14:50.080
I've noticed that the pattern of the ancient mirror in the picture

14:50.330 --> 14:51.860
looks like the Divine Pattern.

14:51.900 --> 14:53.420
It's upside down.

14:55.870 --> 14:58.470
In his letter, Chong Zhao also mentioned that

14:58.500 --> 14:59.840
Zhen Yu has a kind of weird power

14:59.640 --> 15:02.440
[Zhen Yu has a kind of power that is beyond demonic power and is not owned by eternals, demons or humans.]

14:59.840 --> 15:01.550
that is not owned by eternals, demons

15:01.550 --> 15:02.870
or humans.

15:02.870 --> 15:04.520
Why have I never noticed it before?

15:04.570 --> 15:07.170
It's not owned by eternals, demons or humans?

15:07.190 --> 15:08.880
It's also hard to notice this power?

15:09.000 --> 15:10.420
Could it be...

15:11.560 --> 15:12.600
the hidden power?

15:13.030 --> 15:14.440
That's impossible.

15:14.440 --> 15:16.630
The Hidden Race became extinct 60,000 years ago.

15:17.060 --> 15:19.170
How could the hidden power still exist in the world?

15:19.360 --> 15:22.270
But what if the hidden power still exists?

15:24.550 --> 15:25.550
Could it be that

15:25.590 --> 15:27.740
Zhen Yu is a member of the Hidden Race?

15:28.190 --> 15:30.120
I once fought with Zhen Yu.

15:32.120 --> 15:33.790
I'm sure he's a member of the Demon Race.

15:33.820 --> 15:35.300
Then the reason must be that

15:35.320 --> 15:37.530
he got the hidden power in a certain way,

15:37.700 --> 15:39.840
and he has been plotting it secretly all these years.

15:39.860 --> 15:41.380
What has he been plotting?

15:42.930 --> 15:43.870
It's about the Divine Mirror

15:43.870 --> 15:45.150
and the hidden power.

15:45.550 --> 15:46.710
Can't you think of anything?

15:46.730 --> 15:47.570
What is it?

15:47.600 --> 15:48.830
Tell me!

15:48.850 --> 15:52.100
The hidden power can be used to combine the power of eternals and demons.

15:52.230 --> 15:53.680
Then with the help of a divine object,

15:55.020 --> 15:58.380
this person can gain the power that is as strong as a deity's.

15:59.930 --> 16:01.310
Sir, do you mean that

16:01.930 --> 16:02.720
Zhen Yu

16:03.200 --> 16:04.590
wants to become a deity?

16:05.120 --> 16:06.690
I'm still not sure about it.

16:07.260 --> 16:09.490
But we can't afford to take the risk.

16:10.150 --> 16:12.120
Rumor has it that the 72 Sects

16:12.140 --> 16:13.880
will come to Lanling for a meeting.

16:14.110 --> 16:15.540
Senior,

16:15.830 --> 16:16.710
have you forgotten this?

16:17.340 --> 16:19.030
After the riot in Ning'an City last time,

16:19.080 --> 16:20.750
all sects were worried that the war would be out of control.

16:20.750 --> 16:21.720
To ensure the safety of the Human Race,

16:21.720 --> 16:22.790
they don't want to start a war so easily.

16:23.380 --> 16:24.340
No one will come.

16:24.370 --> 16:25.890
This time, it's something related to the Divine Race.

16:25.910 --> 16:27.450
How dare they not come?

16:27.620 --> 16:29.810
If Zhen Yu really becomes a deity,

16:29.840 --> 16:31.250
it will bring a disaster to the Eastern Continent.

16:31.270 --> 16:33.740
All the sects will be eliminated!

16:34.540 --> 16:35.480
Feng Yu.

16:35.770 --> 16:37.140
Go send a message.

16:37.170 --> 16:38.050
Yes.

17:03.170 --> 17:04.599
Every time the Contemplation was absorbed,

17:05.119 --> 17:07.079
the Contemplation Stone could always dissolve the contemplation power.

17:07.560 --> 17:09.000
Why does Baize's Hatred Contemplation

17:09.000 --> 17:10.069
always exist this time?

17:18.950 --> 17:20.480
She has been practicing Eternals' Magic.

17:20.700 --> 17:22.599
The power of eternals and demons cannot be compatible.

17:31.160 --> 17:32.290
Shuo.

17:32.870 --> 17:34.040
I'm here.

17:35.850 --> 17:37.370
I'm always here.

17:41.310 --> 17:42.260
Fan Yue.

17:43.270 --> 17:44.830
She has suffered so much for you.

17:45.590 --> 17:47.030
Not only can you not save her,

17:47.050 --> 17:49.050
but you also can't share her pain.

17:49.980 --> 17:52.100
What's the use of your demonic power?

17:53.680 --> 17:54.640
Shuo.

17:56.290 --> 17:58.550
I'll find a way to save you.

18:01.670 --> 18:02.620
I certainly will.

18:10.800 --> 18:12.300
Aren't I in the Stone Clan?

18:12.460 --> 18:13.570
Where am I now?

18:14.080 --> 18:15.020
Fan Yue!

18:15.280 --> 18:16.410
Fan Yue!

18:16.780 --> 18:17.870
Fan Yue!

18:19.790 --> 18:20.660
Fan Yue!

18:22.140 --> 18:23.180
Fan Yue!

18:23.490 --> 18:24.410
Fan Yue!

18:43.790 --> 18:45.550
Baize's resentment aura entered my body.

18:45.720 --> 18:47.310
So this is my sea of consciousness?

19:12.730 --> 19:13.680
Wood Fortress?

19:14.520 --> 19:16.010
Is this...

19:30.120 --> 19:31.160
Sir.

19:31.190 --> 19:32.120
Is this...

19:32.140 --> 19:33.620
An outsider broke into our fortress!

19:33.650 --> 19:36.220
Someone broke into our fortress! Someone broke into our fortress!

19:36.440 --> 19:37.830
-Who is it?
-Who?

19:37.830 --> 19:39.480
Someone broke into our fortress!

19:40.480 --> 19:41.610
I'm not a bad person.

19:41.640 --> 19:42.590
Guys, don't be afraid.

19:44.270 --> 19:45.180
Who are you?

19:45.200 --> 19:46.130
How did you get in?

19:46.160 --> 19:46.880
Could it be that

19:46.900 --> 19:47.900
you're up to something?

19:48.320 --> 19:50.490
-I…
-She is my guest.

19:57.100 --> 19:59.190
-Hello, Chief.
-Chief.

20:02.990 --> 20:03.840
Kid,

20:03.860 --> 20:05.410
you're finally here.

20:05.960 --> 20:08.250
I've been waiting for you for so long.

20:13.550 --> 20:15.060
Greetings, Lady Tian Huo.

20:15.480 --> 20:17.110
Has Master Fan come back from the Stone Clan?

20:17.110 --> 20:18.510
He's in Ms. Bai's room.

20:18.820 --> 20:19.750
Who is this?

20:21.790 --> 20:22.900
Take her away first.

20:22.930 --> 20:24.020
Take good care of her.

20:27.220 --> 20:28.180
Don't be afraid.

20:28.200 --> 20:29.280
It's very safe here.

20:29.310 --> 20:30.710
They will protect you.

20:33.010 --> 20:33.980
By the way,

20:34.470 --> 20:35.860
why didn't I see Cang Shan

20:35.960 --> 20:37.740
on my way into the palace?

20:38.150 --> 20:39.280
Where is he?

20:58.680 --> 21:00.070
I'll kill you!

21:03.850 --> 21:04.860
Tian Huo.

21:05.060 --> 21:06.100
Calm down.

21:06.130 --> 21:07.920
Cang Shan died because of him.

21:08.230 --> 21:10.120
Why are you still protecting him?

21:10.150 --> 21:11.260
He is your buddy.

21:11.280 --> 21:12.720
Isn't Cang Shan your buddy?

21:12.750 --> 21:15.030
He put evil insects into the bodies of Stone Clan's people.

21:15.370 --> 21:17.290
Although the parent insect died with Cang Shan,

21:17.310 --> 21:19.230
the sub insects are still inside the bodies of Stone Clan's people.

21:19.280 --> 21:20.940
They are still unconscious now.

21:20.960 --> 21:22.700
Only he can force the evil insects out.

21:23.060 --> 21:24.500
He can't die yet.

21:25.200 --> 21:27.030
Take out the evil insects.

21:27.330 --> 21:29.500
Otherwise, I'll kill you now!

21:30.350 --> 21:31.680
I'll die sooner

21:31.960 --> 21:33.250
or later.

21:33.280 --> 21:34.170
Of course I will make those people

21:34.200 --> 21:36.310
from the Stone Clan die with me.

21:40.290 --> 21:41.370
Tian Huo.

21:41.510 --> 21:43.480
Cang Shan died for the Stone Clan.

21:43.760 --> 21:44.510
Once Chen Ye dies,

21:44.550 --> 21:46.170
people of the Stone Clan will never wake up again.

21:51.870 --> 21:53.270
I promise you that

21:53.300 --> 21:54.620
I will help you punish him

21:55.810 --> 21:57.600
for Cang Shan's death.

22:08.820 --> 22:10.500
How are you going to help her punish me?

22:11.020 --> 22:12.070
Will you kill me

22:12.740 --> 22:13.860
or torture me?

22:33.900 --> 22:35.990
[Gu Shang]

22:46.830 --> 22:48.310
Why did you bring me here?

22:48.630 --> 22:49.740
To commemorate them

22:50.180 --> 22:51.220
or apologize?

22:52.500 --> 22:53.450
What?

22:54.110 --> 22:56.510
Do you think you can change me with these things?

22:57.410 --> 22:58.850
Save and awaken the people of the Stone Clan.

22:59.770 --> 23:01.050
Don't make any more mistakes.

23:01.080 --> 23:02.230
Mistakes?

23:02.740 --> 23:03.930
What mistakes did I make?

23:03.960 --> 23:05.370
Don't they deserve to die?

23:05.390 --> 23:06.870
Though the Stone Clan did something wrong,

23:07.500 --> 23:09.450
they've paid a price that is high enough.

23:09.480 --> 23:10.530
It's not enough!

23:10.550 --> 23:12.530
I want all of them to die with me!

23:22.090 --> 23:23.390
What?

23:23.480 --> 23:25.160
You'll stop pretending, huh? Fan Yue.

23:25.890 --> 23:28.580
Stop showing your hypocritical face to me.

23:28.830 --> 23:31.530
I won't spare any member of the Stone Clan.

23:31.330 --> 23:34.860
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

23:31.770 --> 23:33.540
Kill me if you dare!

23:34.510 --> 23:35.550
Kill me!

23:35.750 --> 23:38.110
♫The last moonlight♫

23:36.870 --> 23:38.970
Take revenge for your Cang Shan.

23:39.000 --> 23:40.720
Seek justice for the innocent Stone Clan.

23:39.290 --> 23:42.760
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

23:40.740 --> 23:42.400
Give them an explanation.

23:42.430 --> 23:43.520
Let me tell you.

23:43.540 --> 23:45.340
Not only the evil insects of the Stone Clan

23:43.930 --> 23:46.720
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

23:45.370 --> 23:46.610
but also the Nether Poison in Ning'an City

23:46.650 --> 23:47.930
was made by me.

23:47.250 --> 23:51.410
♫In this life, at this time♫

23:47.960 --> 23:49.810
As for all the people who defied my Grand Master all these years,

23:49.830 --> 23:51.570
I didn't spare any of them!

23:51.600 --> 23:55.070
♫I dare not look back♫

23:55.850 --> 23:59.170
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

24:00.250 --> 24:03.300
♫On your path?♫

24:04.130 --> 24:07.170
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

24:07.700 --> 24:11.020
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

24:11.820 --> 24:13.760
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

24:14.330 --> 24:15.740
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

24:14.730 --> 24:16.560
Why did you stop hitting me?

24:16.110 --> 24:19.400
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

24:16.610 --> 24:18.660
Isn't Cang Shan your good buddy?

24:19.680 --> 24:21.590
How can you take revenge for him if you don't kill me?

24:20.480 --> 24:23.530
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

24:23.380 --> 24:25.030
Anyway, in your mind,

24:23.700 --> 24:26.960
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

24:25.060 --> 24:26.780
they've long been dead.

24:27.650 --> 24:29.970
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

24:28.500 --> 24:30.020
Me, too!

24:30.670 --> 24:32.030
♫Time after time♫

24:32.790 --> 24:37.970
♫Oh, melancholy♫

24:44.410 --> 24:46.110
Cang Shan is my buddy.

24:48.550 --> 24:51.820
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

24:49.440 --> 24:50.640
You, too.

24:52.970 --> 24:55.330
♫The last moonlight♫

24:56.350 --> 24:57.760
Stop lying.

24:56.350 --> 24:59.980
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

24:58.580 --> 25:00.030
Only Tian Huo and Cang Shan

25:00.030 --> 25:02.110
are the capable assistants of the Demon King of the Polar Region.

25:01.150 --> 25:03.780
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

25:02.970 --> 25:04.320
Who am I?

25:04.470 --> 25:08.480
♫In this life, at this time♫

25:05.190 --> 25:07.790
I'm an executioner who did all the bad things,

25:08.080 --> 25:09.670
and I'm Zhen Yu's henchman.

25:08.820 --> 25:12.290
♫I dare not look back♫

25:10.420 --> 25:12.980
How could I deserve to be the buddy of the Master of Bright Moon?

25:12.930 --> 25:16.150
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

25:13.810 --> 25:15.730
No matter what you've become,

25:16.220 --> 25:18.090
and no matter how much you hate me,

25:17.470 --> 25:20.330
♫On your path?♫

25:18.330 --> 25:19.700
you are still my buddy.

25:21.350 --> 25:24.390
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

25:22.520 --> 25:23.940
I'm going to save the Stone Clan

25:24.140 --> 25:25.980
not only for the sake of Cang Shan,

25:24.920 --> 25:28.060
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

25:28.620 --> 25:29.950
but also for the sake of you.

25:29.040 --> 25:30.490
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

25:31.200 --> 25:32.770
The Stone Clan did something wrong.

25:31.550 --> 25:32.500
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

25:32.800 --> 25:34.360
With their sin,

25:33.030 --> 25:36.230
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

25:34.380 --> 25:35.880
as well as fear and anxiety,

25:35.900 --> 25:37.170
they've lived for many years.

25:37.010 --> 25:40.510
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

25:38.120 --> 25:39.090
What about you?

25:40.800 --> 25:44.180
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

25:41.090 --> 25:42.850
Are you also going to live the rest of your life

25:42.880 --> 25:44.740
with hatred among endless killings?

25:44.870 --> 25:46.710
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

25:47.340 --> 25:51.170
♫Time after time♫

25:49.980 --> 25:52.270
Grandfather and my clansmen have already passed away.

25:52.450 --> 25:54.060
You are my only family.

25:54.730 --> 25:55.980
If I could choose,

25:56.110 --> 25:58.620
I would rather be the one that was taken away by the Tiger Clan back then.

25:59.120 --> 26:01.070
I hope that I can bear all the pain

26:01.070 --> 26:02.200
which you've gone through these years.

26:03.900 --> 26:05.320
If only blood can be used to

26:05.350 --> 26:07.250
wipe out the hatred in your heart

26:07.280 --> 26:09.370
so that you can become the same person as you used to be,

26:09.830 --> 26:12.160
after I finish these necessary tasks,

26:12.290 --> 26:13.570
I'll return my life

26:15.290 --> 26:16.280
to you.

26:17.430 --> 26:19.110
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

26:19.710 --> 26:21.310
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

26:21.800 --> 26:25.880
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

26:26.250 --> 26:29.300
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

26:29.610 --> 26:33.200
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

26:33.770 --> 26:35.610
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

26:35.070 --> 26:36.310
[Qi Feng]

26:36.310 --> 26:38.350
[Gu Shang]

26:36.340 --> 26:37.670
♫Time after time♫

26:38.780 --> 26:44.010
♫Oh, melancholy♫

26:43.490 --> 26:44.970
But Fan Yue,

26:46.610 --> 26:48.710
Qi Feng already died a long time ago.

27:23.750 --> 27:25.310
Drinking too much wine is bad for your health.

27:27.160 --> 27:28.440
This is Silly Stone's

27:28.810 --> 27:30.650
favorite peach wine.

27:31.070 --> 27:32.590
I'll drink his wine

27:33.180 --> 27:34.900
for him today.

27:44.250 --> 27:45.970
But in the future,

27:46.860 --> 27:48.160
there won't be any chance for the three of us

27:48.160 --> 27:49.790
to drink together again.

27:51.450 --> 27:52.310
It was my fault.

27:55.930 --> 27:57.880
I failed to protect Cang Shan properly.

28:21.180 --> 28:22.980
If that day,

28:23.220 --> 28:24.890
I had faced the same situation

28:25.930 --> 28:28.390
in the Stone Clan as Silly Stone did,

28:29.240 --> 28:31.670
I would have made the same choice as him.

28:30.430 --> 28:35.210
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

28:38.550 --> 28:44.180
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

28:40.640 --> 28:41.710
However,

28:42.270 --> 28:43.490
I want to ask you a question.

28:43.710 --> 28:46.650
If there were no evil insects in the bodies of Stone Clan's people,

28:46.840 --> 28:54.270
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

28:47.580 --> 28:49.250
would you kill Chen Ye?

28:55.190 --> 29:00.240
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

28:56.810 --> 28:57.910
I don't know.

29:01.450 --> 29:03.580
When the Tiger Clan broke into the Baize Clan back then,

29:04.670 --> 29:06.210
I was the one whom they wanted to catch.

29:07.160 --> 29:08.230
Grandfather

29:08.990 --> 29:10.420
replaced me with Qi Feng.

29:11.430 --> 29:12.400
If it weren't for me,

29:12.400 --> 29:14.510
Qi Feng wouldn't be like this today.

29:15.720 --> 29:17.610
I'm not able to requite evil with good.

29:18.090 --> 29:20.770
Not killing him is the kindest thing I could do.

29:22.180 --> 29:23.050
However,

29:23.900 --> 29:25.490
I want to remind you that

29:25.670 --> 29:27.870
he's Chen Ye now,

29:27.920 --> 29:29.600
and he's no longer Qi Feng whom he used to be.

29:29.630 --> 29:31.850
No matter what you do, you can't change it.

29:32.970 --> 29:34.050
Maybe

29:34.760 --> 29:36.840
he is a calamity in your fate.

29:37.530 --> 29:40.080
Whether to be trapped or let go of it,

29:41.140 --> 29:43.030
you can only rely on yourself to solve this issue.

29:44.230 --> 29:45.440
When I went out this time,

29:45.850 --> 29:47.600
I found out about two things.

29:47.620 --> 29:48.830
The first thing is that

29:49.650 --> 29:51.510
the Taoist who took Bai Xi away back then

29:52.090 --> 29:53.370
came from the Cold Spring Palace.

29:54.730 --> 29:55.740
The second thing is that

29:56.170 --> 29:58.250
there was another orphan from the Tiger Clan back then.

29:58.490 --> 30:00.760
I got some information from her.

30:01.220 --> 30:02.240
I think

30:02.280 --> 30:04.270
you should also hear it.

30:14.700 --> 30:15.800
Master.

30:16.750 --> 30:17.700
What?

30:18.200 --> 30:19.420
You still won't give up?

30:19.670 --> 30:20.910
You still want to

30:20.930 --> 30:22.400
probe into my secret?

30:22.580 --> 30:23.610
You've misunderstood it , Master.

30:24.000 --> 30:25.430
I have no intention of that.

30:25.450 --> 30:27.450
I wonder why you've

30:27.680 --> 30:28.880
summoned me here.

30:29.370 --> 30:30.410
Chong Zhao.

30:31.510 --> 30:32.750
You've been in my Cold Spring Palace

30:32.770 --> 30:34.190
for a period of time.

30:34.730 --> 30:35.860
Does Lanling

30:36.000 --> 30:37.960
really not care about

30:37.960 --> 30:38.920
whether you're dead or alive?

30:43.740 --> 30:45.210
I've joined Cold Spring.

30:45.690 --> 30:47.540
I have nothing to do with Lanling anymore.

30:48.290 --> 30:50.570
Are you really that resolute

30:50.870 --> 30:52.770
or are you pretending to be resolute

30:52.800 --> 30:54.100
in front of me?

30:54.310 --> 30:56.380
I was forced to kill an Eternal by Fu Ling.

30:56.570 --> 30:58.080
I've long violated the Eternals' rules

30:58.110 --> 30:59.500
and been despised by the Eternals.

31:00.030 --> 31:01.430
I have nowhere to go.

31:01.460 --> 31:03.470
Since the Cold Spring Palace has taken me in,

31:03.710 --> 31:05.510
I will only serve Cold Spring

31:05.530 --> 31:06.660
and work for you.

31:13.040 --> 31:14.240
Chong Zhao.

31:14.690 --> 31:15.900
You should know that

31:16.810 --> 31:17.860
I could have

31:18.120 --> 31:19.160
killed you

31:19.190 --> 31:20.500
several times.

31:21.770 --> 31:23.310
You can live till now

31:23.460 --> 31:25.170
not because of your own power,

31:25.440 --> 31:26.640
but because of

31:26.670 --> 31:28.240
my mercy to you.

31:29.720 --> 31:32.260
Lanling has claimed to be kind and righteous.

31:32.720 --> 31:34.290
But they don't care about

31:34.310 --> 31:36.360
your safety at all.

31:37.330 --> 31:38.650
They always talk about

31:38.680 --> 31:41.260
protecting the people of the world.

31:41.360 --> 31:42.910
But in my opinion,

31:43.060 --> 31:44.650
they are all hypocrites.

31:45.760 --> 31:47.430
In the future, you'll know

31:47.450 --> 31:48.340
who

31:48.370 --> 31:50.330
really cares about you.

31:51.040 --> 31:52.440
It's my luck that

31:52.470 --> 31:54.050
you trust me.

31:54.140 --> 31:55.550
I'll definitely...

32:01.240 --> 32:02.580
Since you want to be

32:02.610 --> 32:04.860
a strong man by my side,

32:04.880 --> 32:06.040
firstly,

32:06.070 --> 32:07.460
I want you to

32:07.480 --> 32:09.610
cut your tie with the Eternal Race completely.

32:25.170 --> 32:27.730
As long as you have demonic power in your body,

32:27.770 --> 32:29.330
you will never be able to

32:29.370 --> 32:31.400
be a real Eternal again.

32:32.560 --> 32:34.080
Secondly,

32:34.100 --> 32:35.790
I want you to practice

32:36.610 --> 32:38.880
the magic of combining the power of eternals and demons.

32:41.370 --> 32:42.930
How can the power of

32:43.320 --> 32:44.910
eternals and demons be combined?

32:45.510 --> 32:46.480
No hurry.

32:46.950 --> 32:49.190
You will know it soon.

32:57.330 --> 32:58.380
Chong Zhao!

33:03.430 --> 33:05.080
Did Grand Master punish you?

33:07.030 --> 33:08.100
Is there any way

33:08.120 --> 33:09.830
to suck out the demonic power in my body?

33:10.120 --> 33:10.980
Demonic power?

33:11.480 --> 33:13.130
Zhen Yu infused demonic power into my body.

33:13.150 --> 33:15.270
He wants me to completely degenerate into a demon!

33:15.740 --> 33:17.580
The magic of eternals and demons is incompatible.

33:17.610 --> 33:18.330
Doing this

33:18.350 --> 33:19.460
will only damage your foundation

33:19.510 --> 33:20.330
and make you die.

33:20.350 --> 33:22.020
What exactly does Grand Master want to do?

33:22.050 --> 33:23.620
I need to force the demonic power out.

33:23.850 --> 33:25.220
I'm a member of the Eternal Race.

33:25.480 --> 33:26.310
I can't become a demon.

33:26.310 --> 33:27.530
I still have to go back to Lanling.

33:28.290 --> 33:29.200
Hurry up.

33:29.220 --> 33:30.170
Help me!

34:09.070 --> 34:10.120
It's useless.

34:10.139 --> 34:11.340
It looks like forcing it out

34:11.360 --> 34:13.190
will only accelerate the damage of the foundation.

34:13.800 --> 34:15.429
At this point,

34:15.449 --> 34:16.489
you can't restore it.

34:18.580 --> 34:19.500
Chong Zhao.

34:19.219 --> 34:22.230
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

34:20.489 --> 34:21.690
Leave here.

34:21.940 --> 34:22.940
Go find Jin Yao.

34:22.810 --> 34:25.400
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

34:22.969 --> 34:24.050
He must have a way.

34:24.070 --> 34:25.179
I can't.

34:26.139 --> 34:30.120
♫I remember that word of concern♫

34:27.030 --> 34:29.429
I haven't figured out Zhen Yu's secret completely.

34:29.460 --> 34:31.330
Look at you now.

34:30.639 --> 34:33.900
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

34:31.350 --> 34:32.929
You're neither an eternal nor a demon.

34:33.290 --> 34:34.850
Grand Master clearly knew that you came to the Cold Spring Palace

34:34.469 --> 34:37.250
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

34:34.880 --> 34:36.320
to gather information.

34:36.850 --> 34:37.770
If he didn't kill you,

34:37.800 --> 34:39.429
he must have a reason to torture you.

34:38.050 --> 34:41.310
♫It dried in the wind♫

34:39.449 --> 34:40.699
I've been in the Cold Spring Palace for so long.

34:40.730 --> 34:42.780
I've never heard of the Magic of Eternals and Demons.

34:41.900 --> 34:43.699
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

34:42.840 --> 34:43.810
If you don't leave now,

34:43.830 --> 34:45.350
there will be no chance.

34:44.170 --> 34:47.830
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

34:46.199 --> 34:47.739
You're the one who should leave.

34:48.540 --> 34:51.870
♫That year, that year♫

34:48.900 --> 34:51.150
You've done enough for him.

34:52.560 --> 34:55.909
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

34:52.710 --> 34:54.110
Leave here

34:54.250 --> 34:56.210
and live a free life.

34:56.350 --> 34:59.790
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

34:57.690 --> 34:58.650
Maybe...

35:00.510 --> 35:02.990
Maybe you can still find your family.

35:00.850 --> 35:03.260
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

35:04.040 --> 35:07.300
♫That year, that year♫

35:04.230 --> 35:05.590
Family?

35:05.650 --> 35:06.860
What do you mean?

35:08.130 --> 35:11.080
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

35:08.400 --> 35:09.210
Chong Zhao.

35:09.230 --> 35:10.350
Chong Zhao, how are you?

35:11.790 --> 35:14.820
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

35:12.050 --> 35:14.010
There's no turning back for me.

35:14.260 --> 35:15.940
Leave now!

35:16.040 --> 35:18.640
♫Layer after layer♫

35:21.770 --> 35:23.080
There's no turning back

35:23.100 --> 35:24.420
for all the people in the Cold Spring Palace.

35:25.450 --> 35:27.020
Since we can't go back to the past,

35:26.030 --> 35:29.460
♫That year, that year♫

35:27.820 --> 35:29.370
let's just face it together.

35:30.170 --> 35:33.380
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

35:34.170 --> 35:37.350
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

35:37.990 --> 35:40.680
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

35:41.520 --> 35:44.870
♫That year, that year♫

35:45.360 --> 35:48.540
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

35:49.390 --> 35:52.200
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

35:53.900 --> 35:56.240
♫Layer after layer♫

35:56.890 --> 35:59.910
♫Another year passed♫

36:04.110 --> 36:08.240
♫Another year passed♫

36:13.370 --> 36:14.530
Just answer

36:14.560 --> 36:15.690
whatever Master Fan asks.

36:15.100 --> 36:16.410
[Nuo, Demon Race, Daughter of the Tiger King]

36:17.970 --> 36:19.750
So you are the orphan of the Tiger King?

36:21.440 --> 36:22.330
What's your name?

36:22.350 --> 36:23.350
My name is...

36:23.380 --> 36:24.340
Nuo.

36:24.880 --> 36:26.990
Who eliminated the Tiger Clan back then?

36:27.540 --> 36:28.190
It was...

36:29.270 --> 36:31.340
eliminated by a demon lord sitting in a wheelchair.

36:32.740 --> 36:33.720
That's absurd!

36:34.260 --> 36:36.530
Although the Tiger Clan wasn't the head of the Demon Race,

36:36.560 --> 36:38.500
few demons could kill the Tiger King.

36:38.530 --> 36:39.800
Since that demon lord was sitting in a wheelchair,

36:39.800 --> 36:41.070
how could he eliminate the whole Tiger Clan?

36:41.100 --> 36:42.720
My memory of it can't be wrong.

36:47.600 --> 36:48.380
Father.

36:49.090 --> 36:49.820
Father.

36:49.850 --> 36:51.460
Father, what happened?

36:52.700 --> 36:54.410
They came quite suddenly.

36:54.880 --> 36:56.730
The entire Tiger Clan was defenseless.

36:57.560 --> 36:59.890
My father hid me in a secret chamber behind the throne.

36:59.910 --> 37:01.630
That was why I wasn't killed.

37:42.610 --> 37:44.320
I escaped death that night.

37:44.760 --> 37:47.240
Since then, I've been hiding my identity and living in the Human Race.

37:47.260 --> 37:49.160
And I didn't dare to step into the Demon Race again.

37:49.810 --> 37:50.710
Until...

37:51.910 --> 37:53.720
Until Lady Tian Huo found me.

37:54.310 --> 37:55.440
Do you still remember the face

37:56.170 --> 37:57.430
of that demon lord?

38:16.880 --> 38:17.840
What?

38:19.960 --> 38:21.050
Are you here to kill me?

38:22.370 --> 38:23.580
It was you

38:23.600 --> 38:24.880
who killed my father

38:24.900 --> 38:26.270
and all the people of the Tiger Clan!

38:26.300 --> 38:28.340
I can't believe that there's still a survivor from the Tiger Clan.

38:39.110 --> 38:41.150
The murderer who eliminated the Baize Clan is right in front of us.

38:41.180 --> 38:42.570
How dare you protect her?

38:42.590 --> 38:43.790
She was still young back then.

38:44.360 --> 38:45.360
She's not the murderer.

38:45.400 --> 38:46.400
Fan Yue.

38:47.220 --> 38:49.140
You are so kind-hearted.

38:49.600 --> 38:51.330
Have you forgotten

38:51.650 --> 38:53.000
how the old people, weak people, women and children

38:53.030 --> 38:55.160
of the Baize Clan were killed tragically by the Tiger Clan?

38:56.210 --> 38:57.950
I was the one who eliminated the Tiger Clan.

38:58.410 --> 38:59.930
I took revenge for the Baize Clan.

38:59.960 --> 39:01.170
What did you do?

39:01.590 --> 39:03.280
Now you're still pretending to be righteous here.

39:03.300 --> 39:04.080
Enough!

39:05.660 --> 39:07.410
Haven't you killed enough people?

39:13.750 --> 39:14.950
Tell me.

39:15.880 --> 39:18.180
Why did the Tiger Clan search for the boy with purple pupils?

39:18.770 --> 39:20.600
I don't know anything about the boy with purple pupils.

39:21.260 --> 39:22.400
I only know that

39:22.880 --> 39:25.380
there was a mysterious person who occasionally met my father.

39:26.040 --> 39:27.410
After they met every time,

39:27.810 --> 39:29.730
the Tiger Clan would take action accordingly.

39:30.240 --> 39:31.430
Who is this mysterious person?

39:31.930 --> 39:33.390
I've never seen his face.

39:33.990 --> 39:35.800
Nor do I know who he is.

39:36.940 --> 39:37.950
But at one time, while this mysterious person

39:38.000 --> 39:39.630
was discussing something with my father in a room,

39:40.170 --> 39:41.560
I accidentally intruded into the room.

39:41.590 --> 39:42.470
Father!

39:44.550 --> 39:45.280
My Lord.

39:45.320 --> 39:46.220
This is my daughter.

39:46.240 --> 39:46.990
She is ignorant as a kid.

39:47.020 --> 39:47.630
Please spare her life, My Lord.

39:47.630 --> 39:49.410
Although I didn't see the face of that mysterious person,

39:49.850 --> 39:51.110
I saw a black

39:51.150 --> 39:53.000
snake mark on his arm.

39:53.820 --> 39:55.810
A black snake mark?

39:58.040 --> 39:59.560
Are you unwilling to accept the result?

39:59.760 --> 40:01.250
I can help you.

40:16.640 --> 40:17.880
I'll go investigate it now.

40:30.780 --> 40:33.140
I once saw you in Qi Feng's memory.

40:33.250 --> 40:34.810
You're the Chief of the Baize Clan.

40:35.790 --> 40:36.840
You know me?

40:37.480 --> 40:39.160
Baize's resentment aura

40:39.330 --> 40:42.700
was suppressed under the Stone Formation by the Stone Clan.

40:43.090 --> 40:45.160
We couldn't communicate with others.

40:45.300 --> 40:48.070
Fortunately, with the help of the Contemplation Stone,

40:48.100 --> 40:50.100
we're able to talk to you now.

40:51.180 --> 40:52.450
I know

40:52.660 --> 40:54.840
you're Bai Shuo.

40:55.280 --> 40:58.030
I also know your relationship with Yue.

40:58.050 --> 40:59.340
Logically speaking,

40:59.620 --> 41:00.870
you should

41:00.890 --> 41:02.860
call me Grandfather.

41:04.750 --> 41:06.450
Greetings, Grandfather.

41:07.260 --> 41:09.480
With you staying by Yue's side,

41:09.620 --> 41:11.410
I feel relieved.

41:13.620 --> 41:15.580
Fan Yue has always missed you guys.

41:15.600 --> 41:17.350
There is a secret chamber in the Bright Moon Palace,

41:17.380 --> 41:19.630
and the nameplates of the entire Baize Clan are hung there.

41:19.950 --> 41:21.830
He has never forgotten you guys.

41:21.890 --> 41:24.030
Even when he lost his memory in Outlanders' City,

41:24.060 --> 41:25.540
you guys were always in his dreams.

41:26.160 --> 41:27.390
If he can't forget us,

41:27.410 --> 41:29.400
it's not necessarily a good thing.

41:31.820 --> 41:33.700
The more he can't let go of it,

41:33.730 --> 41:35.880
the more suffering and pain

41:35.990 --> 41:37.550
he'll experience.

41:37.690 --> 41:39.230
That's the case for Yue.

41:39.470 --> 41:42.090
And it's the same for Qi Feng, too.

41:42.620 --> 41:44.340
Cang Shan

41:44.610 --> 41:46.480
sacrificed his own life

41:46.620 --> 41:49.160
to dissolve Baize's resentment aura.

41:49.410 --> 41:51.220
That was not what I wanted.

41:52.900 --> 41:53.970
However,

41:54.000 --> 41:55.810
I couldn't stop it.

41:56.960 --> 41:58.690
My clansmen and I

41:59.310 --> 42:00.630
will soon

42:00.660 --> 42:02.570
disappear from the world.

42:03.050 --> 42:04.660
There are some things

42:04.930 --> 42:07.270
I have to let you guys know.

42:07.740 --> 42:08.730
So,

42:08.900 --> 42:12.620
with the opportunity of the Contemplation Stone absorbing your Contemplation,

42:13.200 --> 42:15.200
I brought all the souls of our clansmen

42:15.220 --> 42:17.970
into your sea of consciousness.

42:18.250 --> 42:19.810
What do you want to tell me, Grandfather?

42:20.450 --> 42:21.970
A truth.

42:22.000 --> 42:24.480
It's the truth that you guys have been wanting to know,

42:25.230 --> 42:28.180
which is about the boy with purple pupils.
